data.description: Great ranch sitting on 1+ acres, provides so many possibilities and room for expansion!!  This home is ready for your vision, complete with living room, large eat in kitchen, three bedrooms, one bath,mudroom/laundry room and attached one car garage.  Conveniently located with easy access to major highways, shopping, schools, parks and so much more!
